item.description:
1.总体思路 在搭建验证框架时经常要输入很多重复性的代码，有两种快速获得验证的方法，一种是复制原有的框架代码，在代码上面修改，一种是利用脚本语言快速生成代码。本文通过python脚本，快速生成agent的代码，提高工作效率。2.python脚本 利用open、write函数创建SV文件，写入UVM框架代码。code_gen.py:#coding=utf-8 import sys name = input(&quot;input agentname:
&quot;) f = open(name+&quot;_pkg.sv&quot;, 'w+', encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;) f.write(&quot;`include \&quot;uvm_macros.svh\&quot;

&quot;) f.write(&quot;package &quot;+name+&quot;_pkg;

&quot;) f.write(&quot;import uvm_pkg::*;

&quot;) name_trans = name + &quot;_trans&quot; f.write(&quot;class &quot;+name_trans+&quot; extends uvm_sequence_item;
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	function new(string name=\&quot;&quot;+name_trans+&quot;\&quot;);
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		super.new(name);
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	endfunction

&quot;) f.write(&quot;	//输入变量
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	rand ;
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	rand ;
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	`uvm_object_utils_begin(&quot;+name_trans+&quot;)
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		`uvm_field_
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		`uvm_field_
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	`uvm_object_utils_end
&quot;) f.write(&quot;
endclass
&quot;) name_seq = name+&quot;_seq&quot; f.write(&quot;
class &quot;+name_seq+&quot; extends uvm_sequence;
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	`uvm_object_utils(&quot;+name_seq+&quot;)

&quot;) f.write(&quot;	function new(string name=\&quot;&quot;+name_seq+&quot;\&quot;);
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		super.new(name);
&quot;) f.write(&quot;	endfunction

&quot;) f.write(&quot;	virtual task body();
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		&quot;+name_trans+&quot; tr;
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		repeat(10) begin
&quot;) f.write(&quot;			`uvm_do(tr)
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		end
&quot;) f.write(&quot;		endtask
&quot;) f.write(&quot;endclass

&quot;) name_sqr = name+&quot;_sqr&quot; f.
